<aside class="author-bio" aria-label="About the author">
  <div class="author-bio__avatar" aria-hidden="true"><span>JL</span></div>
  <div class="author-bio__body">
    <span class="author-bio__label">Written by</span>
    <h3 class="author-bio__name">Jeremy Lim</h3>
    <p class="author-bio__role">Founder &amp; Lead Tutor, A-Worthy &middot; LLB (Hons), NUS Faculty of Law</p>
    <p class="author-bio__desc">Jeremy founded A-Worthy after a career in corporate law and built the SHARP Method to bring the analytical rigour of legal training into Singapore&rsquo;s tuition rooms. He has personally coached over 500 students across O-Level English &amp; Maths, H1 General Paper, and H2 Economics.</p>
    <a class="author-bio__link" href="/about/">Read Jeremy&rsquo;s story &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</aside>

